Just like the first season, this one has 49 episodes. In the first part of the season it is the rest of the World Duel Carnival & the rest of the season are the Barians making their moves on destroying Astral World. The ending of this season is that Yuma & Astral obtain a new power, summon Utopia Ray Victory & use it to defeat Vector in a duel.
